commenter.bio: I'm just streaming my games.  Generally between 6pm and 10pm GMT, but there is no hard schedule.  Feel free to say hi and tell me how I'm playing wrong.

message.body: @edbot300 Valid inputs are A, B, Z, L, R, Start, CUp, CDown, CLeft, CRight (C buttons), DUp, DDown, DLeft, DRight (D-Pad, unused in most games), Up, Down, Left and Right (Analog stick, used in almost every game as the standard movement input). Typos
